{"tid":2022401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許智峯被保安襲擊, 胸壁受傷","createTime":"2020-05-18T10:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T11:08:34.000Z","uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2edd71f6d049e37261dfb2489d813996dd19d02e","tid":2022401,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/huichifung913/photos/a.402989486549920/1505835759598615/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhuichifung913%2Fphotos%2Fa.402989486549920%2F1505835759598615%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCkwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=4c59fcc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/huichifung913/photos/a.402989486549920/1505835759598615/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n許智峯 Ted Hui Chi Fung<br />\n37分鐘 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n今早內會衝突，我一度被黑保安施以黑警四招呼：壓頭、壓頸、壓心口、壓腿。雖然今日會議較密，但我因仍有點不適，下午去了醫院檢查及照X光，醫生指我胸壁受傷。儘管如此，議會抗爭之路艱難重重，我們仍無懼怕，未來會繼續抗爭到底。<br />\n<br />\n #建制派霸王硬上弓 #內會黑哨 #議會抗爭 #港島許智峯"},{"pid":"8d6dd2ff0190f5a86812b48a214e20e28f62ffd7","tid":2022401,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb090f3fb44bbc40df7b5a2e96332e9bf4a19be5","tid":2022401,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21eb309712d238706e84593e1a242b60777fd3ea","tid":2022401,"uid":219269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:06:17.000Z","msg":"許勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25729a90f2422cae02d6ff683eb877d096a3a5c0","tid":2022401,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ephmedia.giphy.com/777593db-8a51-4b4f-8f44-f715ef6ac812.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h